        nextPoint7 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Data Structure and Algorithm Analysis and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
        nextPoint8 - Act as a mark if student chooses "Yes" for Computer System Organization and provide valid reason where student have taken Computer System Organization which is the pre-requisite for Operating System and Basic Networking.
        nextPoint9 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Computer System Organization and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
        nextPoint10 - Act as a mark if student chooses "Yes" for System Analysis and Design and provide valid reason where student have taken System Analysis and Design which is the pre-requisite for Information Technology Project Management.
        nextPoint11 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for System Analysis and Design and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
        nextPoint12 - Act as a mark if student chooses "Yes" for Mathematics for IT and provide valid reason where student have taken Mathematics for IT which is the pre-requisite for Discrete Structure.
        nextPoint13 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Mathematics for IT and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
        nextPoint14 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Logic Programming and provide valid reason where student have not taken the majoring core.
        nextPoint15 - Act as a mark if student chooses "Yes" for Knowledge Discovery in Database and provide valid reason where student have taken Knowledge Discovery in Database which is the pre-requisite for Neural Network and Machine Learning.
        nextPoint16 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Knowledge Discovery in Database and provide valid reason where student have not taken the majoring core.
        nextPoint17 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Expert System and provide valid reason where student have not taken the majoring core.
        nextPoint18 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Statistics for IT and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
        nextPoint19 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Human Computer Interaction and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
        nextPoint20 - Act as a mark if student chooses "No" for Programming 2 and provide valid reason where student have not taken the program core.
